# Hanzify Web App

This web service transliterates any given name into Chinese according to official standard. So far only Russian names are supported. The name can be supplied using the form on this page or directly in the URL (the result will be shown on separate page).

All bugs can be reported and issues can be discussed at the [official GitHub repository](https://github.com/infusiastic/hanzifyapp).

The app can be accessed at the [official hosting location](http://hanzify.infusiastic.me).

